COMPILATION
===========

In order to compile Echo, you need to obtain XOM (http://www.xom.nu/unstable.html)
To compile:
  $ ant -Dfreenet-cvs-snapshot.location=/path/to/freenet-cvs-snapshot.jar

To build the javadoc:
  $ ant javadoc


RUNNING
=======

Visit the plugins page ("http://127.0.0.1:8888/plugins/ by default) with your Web browser.

In the Load Plugin box, enter: *@file:///path/to/Echo.jar and click the Load button.

Then click the Visit button.